    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus domni ************* pape sede anno primo,
                        inperatore nondum abemus, Enricus defunctus, in Italia nulus inperat in Dei
                        nomine, [die] quinto m(ense) ienuario, ind(itjone) detjma, <placeName
                            ref="#places/4179">Panposia</placeName>. Petivit at vo(s) quidem in
                        [Dei] nomine domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1597"
                            >Albizo</persName> gr(atj)a Dei <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Land_clearing #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Penalty #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Linen #Canals #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie</orgName>, consensum fratrum,
                        largitore uti me pre(sente) in Dei nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/de Caput Caneti">Ihoannes qui vocatur de
                                    <placeName>Caput Caneti</placeName></name></persName> meisque
                        filiis et heredibus <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libell(um)
                            nomine</rs> concedistis et largistis atque confirmastis rem iuris
                        suprascripto monasterio vestrum, idest concedistis me suprascripto petitore
                        medietatem de tres partes de <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> ubi abitare viso
                        sum, ipsum casale quod est in lognitudinem sua de <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Casalia" ref="#places/3563">Gauro</placeName> in <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">vale</rs> quod usque scodere potuerimus:
                        ab uno latere <persName key="#Casalia #Confinia"><name ref="Iustinus"
                                >Iustino</name></persName>, alio latere <persName
                            key="#Casalia #Confinia"><name ref="Ursus/Mulenario">Urso qui vocatur
                                Mulenario</name></persName>, tercio <rs key="#Canals">canale</rs>
                        qui vocatur de <geogName key="#Confinia #Casalia #Canals"
                            ref="#estates/2456"><placeName key="#Confinia #Casalia #Canals"
                                >Falce</placeName></geogName> atque a quarto latere Gauro percurens;
                        pro suprascripto casalem pensione[m] dare debeamus onnique anno in
                        asunsionem sancte Marie <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denarios Veneticorum
                            quinque</rs>, tantum pensio ut dictum est persolvatur. Et insuper
                        concedistis me ipsa por[ci]onem que at suprascripta parte de casale pertinet
                        infra totum <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Land_clearing #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Linen #Levies"
                            ref="#estates/3927"><placeName
                                key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Land_clearing #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Forests #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Linen #Levies"
                                ref="#places/4685">Medio Gauro</placeName></geogName>, quod est a
                        primo latere de <placeName key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Confinia">pulitjno quod reiacet de supra</placeName>
                         in Gauro perveniente per <placeName key="#Forests #Confinia"
                            >tumba de fraseno</placeName> usque supra capite de <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Land_clearing">ronco</placeName> de <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Confinia #Land_clearing"><name ref="Dominicus de Cavalli">Dominicus de
                                Cavalli</name></persName> quod reiacet in loco qui ditjtur
                            <placeName key="#Casalia #Confinia">Fronti</placeName>, deinde estra
                        verso desendente in <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">pantano</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Casalia #Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">Sancto
                            Ieorio</placeName> iusta <rs key="#Confinia #Fruits/vegetables"
                            >nexpulo</rs>, secundo latere pantano percorente in <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Confinia">rio</rs>, tertjo rio percorente in Gauro cum
                        introito et esito suo atque a quarto latere Gauro percorente; et de ipsa <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Production">tera llaboratoria</rs>
                        <rs key="#Levies">teratico</rs> dare debeatis de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >grano</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">sicale</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">misturia ingranata</rs>, <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> in
                        campo capa quinta at area traendas, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                        >trisico</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores">mileo</rs> in area modio hoctavo,
                            <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> manipula octava, <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs>
                        anfora quarta, semel vice arbore pecto ponendo; si vinea pastinavero estra
                        casale, fruere debeo annos tres; si roncavero et de padule de sue gravero
                        fruere debeo similiter tres, postea redere debeo sicut supra llegitur. Ec
                        omnia concedistis meas ipsum reditum et a ipsa more quod vitjnale libell(um)
                        relegitur suprasedendum, defensandum et meliorandum in annis atvenientibus
                        viginti et nove at renovandum, salva sanatjone domnica dandum libell(um)
                        renovemur. Si quis vero pars nostrum contra ha(nc) libell(um) ire
                        tentaverimus ante perfinitum tempus sicut supra legitur d(et) pars parti
                        fidem servantes ante omnis litis initjum vel interpell(atjonem), pena
                        nomine, <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi untjas duas</rs>, maneat ha(nc)
                        petitjonem in sua firmitate. Quod vero libell(um) uno tinore conscripto
                            <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Hugo">Uguo</name></persName> in Dei
                        nomine <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> de vico qui vocatur Anbrosuus
                        scribendum rogavit et unus alterius nobis pariter iubemus, quod consecuti
                        sumus agamus Deum et nobis masima gr(atj)a. + + + Ssignus manus suprascripto
                        petitore at omnia suprascripta cui relecta est.</ab>
                </div>
